      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Mansour Bin Hazim, from Ibn Abu Yafour, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘When <span class=\"iTxt\">Al-Tala’a</span> (evaporated grape juice) exceeds the third, so it is Prohibited’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Abu Ali al-Ash‘ariy has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Abd al-Jabbar from Mansur ibn Hazim from ibn abu Ya‘fur who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘If al-Tila ’ (the remaining boiled juice) is more than one-third it is unlawful for use.’” "
        ]
      }
